snippet.title: Sam's Journey (C64) · Release Trailer
snippet.description:
IT'S OUT!

Get your own copy of our brand-new C64 platformer from the Protovision online store:

Cardboard Box:

https://www.protovision.games/shop/product_info.php?products_id=199&language=en

Digital Download, Option #1:

https://www.protovision.games/shop/product_info.php?products_id=200&language=en

Digital Download, Option #2:

https://protovision.itch.io/sams-journey

Download the full trailer song by Taxim:
https://www.knightsofbytes.games/media/2017/12/24/TAXIM%20-%20The%20Green%20Hills%20(Sam's%20Journey).mp3
